{"id":4042,"date":"2025-06-11T11:30:56","date_gmt":"2025-06-11T04:30:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4042"},"modified":"2025-06-11T11:30:56","modified_gmt":"2025-06-11T04:30:56","slug":"phuc-hoi-da-sau-di-ung-my-pham","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/phuc-hoi-da-sau-di-ung-my-pham\/","title":{"rendered":"5+ B\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. Khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng. V\u1eady nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m, v\u00e0 l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft s\u1edbm? C\u00f9ng xem ngay b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft <\/span><\/i><b><i>ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m!<\/i><\/b><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phuc-hoi-da-sau-di-ung-my-pham-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ho\u1eb7c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p. Khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t g\u00e2y d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 &#8220;m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda&#8221; v\u00e0 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4043\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4043\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4043\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-1.webp\" alt=\"D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4043\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng kh\u00e1ng th\u1ec3 Immunoglobulin E (IgE), k\u00edch th\u00edch c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da s\u1ea3n sinh Histamine \u2013 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t trung gian g\u00e2y vi\u00eam. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da ng\u1ee9a ng\u00e1y, ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch ho\u1eb7c n\u00f3ng r\u00e1t<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf, ph\u00e1t ban, s\u01b0ng nh\u1eb9<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, bong tr\u00f3c ho\u1eb7c c\u0103ng k\u00edch<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y vi\u00eam da, n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng l\u01b0u \u00fd l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra ngay sau l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ho\u1eb7c t\u00edch l\u0169y theo th\u1eddi gian. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, da m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng. Khi \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra, t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1edf n\u00ean nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n m\u1ed7i khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nguyen-nhan-khien-da-bi-di-ung-my-pham\"><\/span><b>Nguy\u00ean Nh\u00e2n Khi\u1ebfn Da B\u1ecb D\u1ecb \u1ee8ng M\u1ef9 Ph\u1ea9m<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m x\u1ea3y ra khi da ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc, h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5t b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4045\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4045\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4045\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-2.webp\" alt=\"Nguy\u00ean Nh\u00e2n Khi\u1ebfn Da B\u1ecb D\u1ecb \u1ee8ng M\u1ef9 Ph\u1ea9m\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4045\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u1ea7n p<span style=\"font-weight: 400\">h\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/span><\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m: C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da m\u1ecfng, d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng: H\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3, h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9a ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c h\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n m\u1edbi: Da ch\u01b0a quen v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 AHA, BHA, retinol&#8230;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f9ng l\u00fac: Vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-nhan-biet-muc-do-di-ung-my-pham-nhe-hay-nghiem-trong\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m: Nh\u1eb9 hay nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ef1a tr\u00ean th\u1eddi gian ph\u00e1t sinh tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng, d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia th\u00e0nh hai d\u1ea1ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn: d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng t\u1ee9c th\u1eddi v\u00e0 d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng mu\u1ed9n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4046\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4046\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4046\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-3.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4046\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"di-ung-my-pham-tuc-thoi-%e2%80%93-xuat-hien-ngay-sau-khi-tiep-xuc\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m t\u1ee9c th\u1eddi \u2013 Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n ngay sau khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi gian kh\u1edfi ph\u00e1t: Ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i gi\u00e2y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau khi thoa m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft: Da ng\u1ee9a ng\u00e1y, n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf, ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf: \u1ede l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ea3n sinh kh\u00e1ng th\u1ec3 IgE. \u0110\u1ebfn l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac ti\u1ebfp theo, kh\u00e1ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0y k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng, khi\u1ebfn da b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"di-ung-my-pham-muon-%e2%80%93-tich-luy-va-bung-phat-sau-thoi-gian-dai\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m mu\u1ed9n \u2013 T\u00edch l\u0169y v\u00e0 b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t sau th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi gian kh\u1edfi ph\u00e1t: T\u1eeb v\u00e0i gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i \u0111a hai ng\u00e0y sau khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft: V\u00f9ng da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lan r\u1ed9ng, k\u00e8m theo vi\u00eam, s\u01b0ng t\u1ea5y, bong tr\u00f3c ho\u1eb7c m\u1ee5n n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf: Da \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t g\u00e2y d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n m\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t. Khi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i, t\u1ebf b\u00e0o mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch (lympho T) nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n n\u00e0y, g\u00e2y ra vi\u00eam da ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng tr\u00ean di\u1ec7n r\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4047\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4047\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4047\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-4.webp\" alt=\"D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m mu\u1ed9n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4047\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m mu\u1ed9n<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng t\u1ee9c th\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t nhanh ch\u00f3ng n\u1ebfu ng\u1eebng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng mu\u1ed9n th\u01b0\u1eddng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p y khoa \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y da c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng, H\u00e3y ng\u1eebng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ngay v\u00e0 tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phan-biet-di-ung-va-kich-ung-my-pham\"><\/span><b>Ph\u00e2n Bi\u1ec7t D\u1ecb \u1ee8ng V\u00e0 K\u00edch \u1ee8ng M\u1ef9 Ph\u1ea9m<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, nh\u01b0ng d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t:<\/span><\/p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u00edch \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u1ea2nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1edbp s\u1eebng c\u1ee7a da, kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Do h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t g\u00e2y d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4, c\u0103ng, \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n mu\u1ed9n h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e8m theo s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam, ng\u1ee9a ng\u00e1y, m\u1ee5n n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u1ea1m vi \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u1edf v\u00f9ng da ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lan r\u1ed9ng, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-cham-soc-phuc-hoi-da-sau-di-ung-my-pham\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng D\u1eabn Ch\u0103m S\u00f3c &amp;<\/b> <strong>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"xu-ly-nhanh-khi-da-bi-di-ung-my-pham\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">X\u1eed L\u00fd Nhanh Khi Da B\u1ecb D\u1ecb \u1ee8ng M\u1ef9 Ph\u1ea9m<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m, vi\u1ec7c x\u1eed l\u00fd k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c: D\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ea1ch ho\u1eb7c n\u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1i sinh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u1eebng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m: N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eb9, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n d\u1eebng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m g\u00e2y d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 theo d\u00f5i t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng: N\u1ebfu da b\u1ecb d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng do \u00e1nh n\u1eafng, h\u00e3y d\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ecdc trong kh\u0103n s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u0103m kh\u00e1m b\u00e1c s\u0129: N\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c b\u00f4i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phuong-phap-phuc-hoi-da-sau-di-ung-my-pham\"><\/span><b>P<\/b><strong>h\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/strong> c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1eeb v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u00f9y v\u00e0o m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ch\u0103m s\u00f3c. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u, h\u00e3y tu\u00e2n theo c\u00e1c h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4048\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4048\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4048\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-5.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Ph\u00e1p Ph\u1ee5c H\u1ed3i Da Sau D\u1ecb \u1ee8ng M\u1ef9 Ph\u1ea9m\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/39-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4048\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Ph\u00e1p Ph\u1ee5c H\u1ed3i Da Sau D\u1ecb \u1ee8ng M\u1ef9 Ph\u1ea9m<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam-sach-da-dung-cach\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m S\u1ea1ch Da \u0110\u00fang C\u00e1ch<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi da \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4031\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4031\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4031\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5.webp\" alt=\"D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4031\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng t\u1ea9y trang d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u, c\u1ed3n, ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thay v\u00ec d\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00f3ng, h\u00e3y r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e1t ho\u1eb7c n\u01b0\u1edbc mu\u1ed1i sinh l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u00e0m da b\u1ecb kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng th\u00eam.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh d\u00f9ng toner c\u00f3 c\u1ed3n, \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dap-mat-na-thien-nhien-phuc-hoi-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1eafp M\u1eb7t N\u1ea1 Thi\u00ean Nhi\u00ean Ph\u1ee5c H\u1ed3i Da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 nha \u0111am: Gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eadt ong nguy\u00ean ch\u1ea5t: C\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ed9t y\u1ebfn m\u1ea1ch: Gi\u1ea3m ng\u1ee9a r\u00e1t, l\u00e0m m\u1ec1m da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 d\u01b0a leo: Cung c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u00e0m m\u00e1t da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"su-dung-serum-phuc-hoi-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed D\u1ee5ng Serum Ph\u1ee5c H\u1ed3i Da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i serum gi\u00fap da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh h\u01a1n nh\u1edd cung c\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide: L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Panthenol (B5): Gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hyaluronic Acid: C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m, duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i cho da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-ve-da-bang-kem-chong-nang\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o V\u1ec7 Da B\u1eb1ng Kem Ch\u1ed1ng N\u1eafng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1edfi tia UV. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3901\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3901\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3901\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6.webp\" alt=\"B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3901\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, c\u00f3 SPF 30 tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed9i m\u0169, \u0111eo kh\u1ea9u trang khi ra ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y trang k\u1ef9 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh b\u00ed t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng cho ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"duy-tri-che-do-sinh-hoat-khoa-hoc\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy Tr\u00ec Ch\u1ebf \u0110\u1ed9 Sinh Ho\u1ea1t Khoa H\u1ecdc<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong c\u0169ng quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">U\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0102n nhi\u1ec1u rau xanh, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y gi\u00e0u vitamin C, E, gi\u00fap da nhanh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n cay n\u00f3ng, d\u1ea7u m\u1ee1, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u01b0\u1ee3u bia v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch th\u00edch.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c, tr\u00e1nh th\u1ee9c khuya \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft Lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng. H\u00e3y lu\u00f4n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, ki\u1ec3m tra th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c khoa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u1eady nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m, v\u00e0 l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft s\u1edbm? C\u00f9ng xem ngay b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4049,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4042","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4042","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4042"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4042\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4051,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4042\/revisions\/4051"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4049"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4042"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4042"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4042"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}